reviewText: Yes, Gary Null has the answers.  Most folks don't know where to draw the line with vaccines and meds for dogs.  It is clear that Gary knows best what is good for dogs.
Excellent. A must have for anyone that loves their pets. A holistic method for keeping your pets in optimal health.

I highly recommend this video for pet owners!!! I learned far more than expected about pet nutrition and how we are killing our pets with excess carbs such that many pets suffer malnutrition making them succeptible to disease.  If you watch this, it can inspire you to radically alter your pets diet in comparison to what's in the commercial pet foods.
